
Shop tab in admin interface will be enabled automatially when this extension
is active.



Define the account handler options in
aashopaccount.ini.append.php

Set up workflow event handlers:

 * Thank you for your order (shop/checkout)
 * Delivery options (shop confirm order before)

Import and set up anapol_shop_settings
(preferrably under settings tab - admin2
allows to do that from dashboard.

Grant access to shop/buy and anapolshop/buy for users you want to be able to
buy.

Add anapolshop design to a chain of your site designs for user siteaccess.